translations.3107061782700787220: Soccer is a sport played between two teams of eleven players with a spherical ball.
translations.1522474359000830033: Ice hockey is a team sport played on ice, in which skaters use sticks to direct a puck into the opposing team's goal.
translations.5852237943118250891: Basketball is a team sport in which two teams of five players try to score points by throwing a ball through the top of a basketball hoop while following a set of rules.
translations.1485710080190614841: Alpine skiing is the sport or recreation of sliding down snow-covered hills on skis with fixed-heel bindings.
